00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:11,400
<i>[Jingshui Inn]</i>

602
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:14,700
Here you go. Enjoy your food. Enjoy!

603
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,600
Can you imagine that?

604
00:41:19,600 --> 00:41:22,400
At that table, the three are tall, short, fat, and thin.

605
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:24,500
They are actually biological brothers.

606
00:41:24,500 --> 00:41:27,400
Get to the point. What did you find out?

607
00:41:27,400 --> 00:41:29,500
I really did find out something.

608
00:41:29,500 --> 00:41:33,400
In the forest near Qingshi Town, there's a tomb called "Consort's Tomb."

609
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:38,700
Rumor has it that when the former dynasty fell, the ruler and his beloved noble consort fled.

610
00:41:38,700 --> 00:41:43,400
With warriors escorting them, they escaped with all their gold and silver.

611
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:47,800
When they reached Qingshi Town, they were cornered.

612
00:41:47,800 --> 00:41:52,400
The warriors could only protect the people and not the treasures.

613
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:58,000
So the ruler thought of a heartless plan.

614
00:41:58,000 --> 00:42:01,000
Did he kill his noble consort?

615
00:42:02,200 --> 00:42:04,000
Not only that.

616
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:10,500
After he built the tomb, in order to turn her into a fierce ghost to protect his treasures,

617
00:42:10,500 --> 00:42:14,800
