618
00:42:14,800 --> 00:42:20,000
Then, over the years, greedy people have tried many ways to steal the treasures.

619
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:22,800
But those who go in never come back.

620
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:26,600
Ghosts don't exist. Most of them are demons.

621
00:42:26,600 --> 00:42:30,000
They make trouble masquerading as fierce ghosts.

622
00:42:31,500 --> 00:42:35,900
Then, from what I heard, that demon is extremely powerful.

623
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:41,800
<i>He seems to have made up his mind to go into the tomb.</i>

624
00:42:41,800 --> 00:42:44,600
<i>I was going to slip away in the name of snooping around,</i>

625
00:42:44,600 --> 00:42:47,600
<i>but the story of the tomb is way too exciting.</i>

626
00:42:47,600 --> 00:42:52,400
<i>If I can gain knowledge, I might as well risk my life to accompany this vile person.</i>

627
00:43:00,500 --> 00:43:02,800
<i>Miss, try this.</i>

628
00:43:02,800 --> 00:43:04,200
<i>Come on.</i>

629
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:06,900
I'll leave it here, all right?

630
00:43:14,400 --> 00:43:16,500
Bai Piaoliang, what brings you here?

631
00:43:16,500 --> 00:43:18,600
I heard you talking about the Consort's Tomb.

632
00:43:18,600 --> 00:43:20,000
I wanted to join in on the fun.

633
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:22,500
Moreover, the more people, the better the odds!

634
00:43:22,500 --> 00:43:25,000
Come on! Let me introduce him to you.

635
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:27,900
This is my friend, Tang Zhou.

636
00:43:28,800 --> 00:43:31,700
This is Brother Qi Hu, Brother Qi Niu, and Brother Qi Bao.

637
00:43:31,700 --> 00:43:33,500
This... This is?

638
00:43:33,500 --> 00:43:35,200
Let me introduce these two to you.

639
00:43:35,200 --> 00:43:39,500
They're famous in Jianghu, Qin Mingyang and Jin Hongmian.
